#

Beef and Vegetable Stir-Fry with Soy-Ginger Sauce

$15
400 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

QuickHealthyMain Course

Description

A quick and flavorful stir-fry featuring tender beef and vibrant veggies in a savory soy-ginger sauce.

Ingredients

  • Beef sirloin: 1 pound
  • Broccoli florets: 2 cups
  • Bell pepper: 1, sliced
  • Carrot: 1, sliced
  • Soy sauce: 1/4 cup
  • Fresh ginger: 1 tablespoon, grated
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Sesame oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Green onions: 2, chopped
  • Vegetable oil: 2 tablespoons
